  "text": "Samsung Galaxy Watch 7 $210 $300 Save $90 The latest version of Samsung's popular wearable, the Galaxy Watch 7, delivers on all fronts and is now even cheaper thanks to this steep discount that drops it down to its best price yet. We've seen some heavy discounts on the Galaxy Watch 7 over the past few months, but nothing beats this deal that drops it down to $210. Samsung's latest smartwatch is a culmination of what the brand has been doing in the wearables space for the past few years, offering a refined product that delivers on all fronts. For this reason and more, it sits at the top of our list as the best smartwatch you can buy in 2025. Related What's great about the Samsung Galaxy Watch 7? You're getting the latest hardware from Samsung with the Galaxy Watch 7 featuring a 1.3-inch AMOLED display and the brand's Exynos W1000 SoC that's paired with 2GB of RAM and 32GB of internal storage. This particular model comes in at 40mm, and also features a nice cream color that can be dressed up or down, depending on the occasion. Since this is a smartwatch, you're not only going to get a sleek look, but it's also quite functional as well, with the wearable being able to track a variety of metrics thanks to its wealth of sensors. It can monitor your heart rate, sleep quality, stress level, and track physical activities. There's also GPS, so you can log your runs, or stay on track during hikes. And since this watch is powered by Google's Wear OS, you have access to a huge app library, making the watch quite versatile. For the most part, you can't go wrong with the Galaxy Watch 7 if you've been thinking about buying a new smartwatch. This is the best price we've seen for this watch, which makes it the perfect time to pick one up. Get this deal before it's gone.",
